'''Jeff Gaffner''' is an award-winning American [[vintner]] from the state of [[California]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.saxonbrown.com/about|title=About {{!}} Saxon Brown Wines|last=vinagency.com|first=Vin,|website=www.saxonbrown.com|language=en|access-date=2018-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.myajc.com/lifestyles/food--cooking/winemaker-the-year-jeff-gaffner/MihSiIRzrQ39xTGotarysO/|title=Winemaker of the Year: Jeff Gaffner|work=myajc|access-date=2018-09-29|language=en}}</ref> His career as a winemaker started in 1981 at Chateau St. Jean under the guidance of Richard Arrowood. In 1997 he started Saxon Brown. Along with Saxon Brown, he has received critical acclaim as the consulting winemaker for high end boutique labels including Xtant, Hestan, and Black Kite Cellars.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xtantwines.com/winemaking/|title=Winemaking - Xtant Wines|last=www.kreck.com|first=Kreck Designs|website=www.xtantwines.com|access-date=2018-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hestanvineyards.com/Team.cfm|title=Hestan Vineyards - Team|website=www.hestanvineyards.com|access-date=2018-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.myajc.com/lifestyles/food--cooking/winemaker-the-year-jeff-gaffner/MihSiIRzrQ39xTGotarysO/|title=Winemaker of the Year: Jeff Gaffner|work=myajc|access-date=2018-09-29|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://kapaluawineandfoodfestival.com/guests/jeff-gaffner/|title=Jeff Gaffner|work=Kapalua Wine and Food Festival|access-date=2018-09-29|language=en-US}}</ref>

